tyle=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n周圍呃人錢 重要借人手機唔還， 整死人地隻倉鼠<br />\n<br />\n我送埋倉鼠糧畀佢 攞到佢屋企 佢都可以 餓死隻倉鼠<br />\n<br />\n佢爭我個friend三千蚊<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢會無端端去人屋企<br />\n<br />\n之前無端端星期日 去我屋企 話搭咗五百蚊的士 過嚟要我畀返佢<br />\n<br />\n旺角搭返嚟屯門先180<br />\n<br />\n一瞓醒冇咗五百蚊<br />\n<br />\n去阿妹周圍呃錢 又爭我錢有爭我朋友錢<br />\n<br />\n仲要整死 人哋隻倉鼠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我送埋倉鼠糧畀佢 佢可以餓死隻倉鼠<br />\n<br />\n借人哋部手機唔還<br />\n<br />\n本身我以為佢會改 點知今日又搵人 私聊我 話吹雞打我<br />\n<br />\n仲要佢 個妹 出街次次冇帶錢 都問我同埋 我個friend借<br />\n<br />\n之前我個friend還返錢畀我 將啲錢放喺佢嗰度 叫佢畀返我 去全部用曬<br />\n<br />\n之前諗住幫佢慶祝生日 買曬禮物畀佢 朝頭早九點 等到去夜晚十點 佢先話唔畀去佢屋企<br />\n<br />\n仲要我哋喺觀塘 去沙頭角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:08.000Z","msg":"死翻去fb啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40ae8170da57cb0d371df1de4e71aec4cb47158f","tid":1071741,"uid":146435,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:31.000Z","msg":"00後真係垃圾 返大陸啦"},{"pid":"6b58caa6af93284d468f25040903bdcf378d4882","tid":1071741,"uid":13936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:37:38.000Z","msg":"咪理樓主啦 想網絡公審人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8924d413e648cb143e278bdd4653e818dc0d454a","tid":1071741,"uid":187076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:39:28.000Z","msg":"狗屎垃圾都po"},{"pid":"12a4494236dfacab624c1a69233a8fd85ef8947d","tid":1071741,"uid":57862,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T01:39:48.000Z","msg":"小學雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c38e4e4a40eadd04728f4b6305156c7dbec5dd","tid":1071741,"uid":214670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e821657159d4bd6041144a5e94dfc8402c777f1c","